**Common Transformations:**
- May combine with Heat to become [[Phlegm-Fire Harassing the Heart]], characterized by mania and agitation.
- May combine with [[Liver Wind]] to cause seizures, tremors, or convulsions.
- In severe, acute cases, may lead to [[Wind-Stroke]].

