### Similar Patterns

| Feature | PHLEGM (Heart) | Phlegm-Fire Harassing the Heart | Heart Blood Stasis | Spleen Qi Deficiency |
|---------|-----------------|----------------------------------|---------------------|----------------------|
| Mental State | Confusion, depression, stupor | Agitation, mania, insomnia | Irritability, anxiety | Muddled thinking, poor memory |
| Tongue | Swollen, sticky white coat | Red body, sticky yellow coat | Purple body, dark spots | Pale, swollen, teeth marks |
